{"tid":2504604,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"太在意一個人所以變得玻璃心？","createTime":"2021-04-26T04:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T03:51:04.000Z","uid":43486,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1eed322de5d90fe82ff6dfc1a2e20a19fc7042f9","tid":2504604,"uid":43486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n玻璃心的出現，其實是因為人們得不到別人的肯定與認同，因而產生憤怒和挫敗，並以負面方式解讀別人的說話，甚至表現出敵意反應。其次，它源於自我保護，這些心理脆弱的人帶有自卑感，難以肯定自我。由於認為自己某方面的能力不足或表現欠佳，所以他們傾向認為別人的批評是在指責和否定自己。此外，對於低自尊和受過心理創傷的人，玻璃心可作為緩衝保護機制。這些人較其他人更容易有心靈受創，前者經常生活在焦慮中；後者害怕再次受到傷害，行事小心翼翼、敏感多疑。總括而言，玻璃心為人們帶來不少負面的心理影響，因為他們總是活在別人的眼光下，認為其他人都在針對自己。久而久之，他們不能正確認識自己，變得畏首畏尾，不敢表現和挑戰自我，甚至會糾結於自己的錯誤，長期無法釋懷。<br />\n<br />\n轉自<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/人人都有玻璃心/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E5%BF%83%2F&d=D9q%2FqAhMrjKrs4nvjauepHhUmc0vP2awQoWdJLgJf%2FY%3D&h=63956a5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E4%BA%BA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E5%BF%83%2F&h=30f1651a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/人人都有玻璃心/</a>"},{"pid":"5a514613d1d25e9eff7f05096a7143a6f0097fc1","tid":2504604,"uid":138138,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbB3X33HFHG4u9qDCWHdU5xBfK7ZMhxdGW6DbRDuJLLja?filename=z3QKFxp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3QKFxp.gif&h=98bfd2dd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fd071ba386fef9f623d7751adb5b6c4a333cd0df","tid":2504604,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T04:08:24.000Z","msg":"試吓唔好咁玻璃心"},{"pid":"3193cd78a4d2a3198d7fad630392101c0a0ea584","tid":2504604,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score